Troubleshooting Tips
OBS Studio Issues:

Black screen in recording: Check screen capture permissions, restart OBS
No audio: Verify PulseAudio settings in OBS Audio settings
Laggy recording: Lower bitrate to 3000 Kbps, use faster encoder preset
FFmpeg Processing Errors:

Codec not found: Install ubuntu-restricted-extras package
Concatenation fails: Ensure all videos have same codec and resolution
Slow processing: Use -preset fast or -preset veryfast for testing
Python Script Issues:

Module not found: Install missing packages with pip3 install --user <package>
Permission denied: Check file permissions with chmod +x script.py
Subprocess errors: Verify ffmpeg commands work independently in terminal
Common Fixes:

# Reinstall multimedia codecs
sudo apt install --reinstall ubuntu-restricted-extras ffmpeg

# Fix audio issues
pulseaudio --kill && pulseaudio --start

# Clear temporary files
rm -rf /tmp/*.mp4 /tmp/*.png
